---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Request Received | Sydney Anxiety Psychology"
  description="Your request has been received. A telehealth psychologist specialising in anxiety will contact you within 1 business day."
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 560px; text-align: center; padding-top: 4rem;">

      <div style="background: var(--color-accent-light); border-radius: 50%; width: 64px; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; font-size: 1.75rem;">
        &#10003;
      </div>

      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Request received.</h1>

      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">A telehealth psychologist specialising in anxiety will be in touch within <strong>1 business day</strong> to introduce themselves and discuss availability.</p>

      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">You are under no obligation to proceed. The contact is purely to establish whether there is a suitable fit.</p>

      <div class="info-box" style="text-align: left; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <p style="margin-top: 0;"><strong>While you wait — things that will help:</strong></p>
        <ol style="margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>Book a GP appointment for your Mental Health Treatment Plan.</strong> A MHTP from your GP unlocks Medicare rebates — $98.95 off each session with a registered psychologist ($145.25 with an endorsed clinical psychologist). You can start this in parallel with waiting for the psychologist to contact you. <a href="/guides/mental-health-care-plan-sydney/">How to get a MHTP from your GP &rarr;</a></li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>Read what to expect from the first session.</strong> Knowing what typically happens in a first psychology session reduces the anticipation anxiety. <a href="/guides/how-telehealth-psychology-works/">How telehealth psychology sessions work &rarr;</a></li>
          <li><strong>Browse the directory if you want to look at who else is listed.</strong> You are not locked in — the match request is a starting point. <a href="/directory/">Browse the full directory &rarr;</a></li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; text-align: left;">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem;">Useful guides while you wait:</p>
        <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.92rem;">
          <li><a href="/guides/cost-telehealth-psychologist-australia/">What does a telehealth psychologist actually cost?</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/how-to-choose-anxiety-psychologist-telehealth/">What to look for in a psychologist for anxiety</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/bulk-billing-psychologist-sydney/">Is bulk billing available? (honest answer)</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/does-online-therapy-work-for-anxiety/">Does online therapy work? (what the research says)</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary);">If you need urgent support, please contact <strong>Lifeline on 13 11 14</strong> or <strong>Beyond Blue on 1300 22 4636</strong>. This directory is not a crisis service.</p>

      <a href="/" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-accent);">&larr; Back to the directory</a>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
